        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Limestone County has its own character. From the historic downtown square to the newer subdivisions in East Limestone, local cleaning companies understand the mix of older homes that need extra care and newer construction with modern finishes. They know about the pollen that blankets everything in spring and the red clay that tracks through entryways year-round.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Hiring locally also means accountability. When your cleaning company is owned by someone who lives in your community, they have extra motivation to get it right.
        </p>

        <!-- COMPARISON SECTION - Strategic Positioning -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Top-Rated Cleaning Services in Athens, AL</h2>

        <!-- TVCT - Featured -->
