            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">1. The Valley Clean Team</span>
            <span class="ml-3 px-3 py-1 bg-[#FFA985] text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full">⭐ Editor's Choice</span>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
